high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter.
Turn right and walk up to the stove.
Put the butter knife in the front left pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan with the butter knife in it.
Turn left and walk over to the counter.
Put the pan with the knife in it on the upper part of the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a butter knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter on the left of the Stove.
Pick up the gray knife in the back on the counter.
Move over right to the front of the stove.
Place the gray knife in the black pan on the front left burner.
Pick up the pan with knife in it.
Turn left and go to the counter on the right of the dish washer.
Place the pan and the knife in it on the shelf above the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with knife in it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn left, go in front of the stove, turn right
Put the knife into the pan in the front left
Pick up the pan in the front left of the stove
Turn left, go to the counter
Put the pan on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a pan, take the pan to the counter
